title: J.J. Cale Featuring Leon Russell In Session at the Paradise Stud
description:
An audio album made out of the DVD.

Live performance from JJ Cale and Leon Russell recorded in 1979 at the Los Angeles Paradise Studios. 

This performance is the most intimate look at JJ Cale ever. Recorded in 1979 at the Paradise Studios in Los Angeles, this rare and unique session, with Leon Russell on keyboards, has never been seen before, and gives fans the chance to see this unique talent at work in the studio.

File format is mp3 @ 320.
